CAPE TOWN, South Africa, July 6, 2020/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The total number of COVID-19 confirmed cases in the North West Province as of Sunday, 05 July 2020 is 6063, with 1104 recoveries and 36 deaths.



North West province COVID-19 laboratory confirmed cases contribute 3.1% to South Africaâ€™s burden of disease.

